flint (1.13.0-dev-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Implemented Rust-style dense error diagnostics with contextual labels.
  * Added strict Type Checker validation for Array homogeneity and Dict keys.
  * Added Poison Type error recovery to prevent cascading false positives.
  * Added Built-in function arity and type signature validation.
  * Fixed UTF-8 offset calculations for string interpolation diagnostics.

